    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "THE HAGUE, October 6th",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Department of Justice",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Pennsylvania Avenue",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "WASHINGTON D.C.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Dear Mr [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Excuse me please if I misspelled your name, but",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "I never saw it in writing.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "On May 5th at 2.15 P.M. of this year I paid you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "a visit in the F.B.I.offices, where I told you details on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "a certain subject you will surely remember. At the end of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "the conversation I promised you not to talk about it un-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "til I had received word from you whether or not the proper",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "authorities were interested. It was taken for granted that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "a few months might elapse before the answer could be given.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Five months have passed by since then, and as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "the subject has now become active in Europe, I am really",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "anxious to go ahead with it. I have ofcourse tried to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "check the theory on each aspect and while doing so I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "found various complementary as well as fundamental details.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "I have now reached the point however where I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "would like to discuss the whole with an expert and I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "would therefor certainly appreciate to know whether I have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "to consider our agreement on complete silence as still",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "being valid and necessary or not.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "It might be that you are too busy to be able to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "write to me or that the authorities are not interested. As",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "it is not my intention to bother you too much with it, I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "will take it that there is no longer any necessity for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "silence on my part if I do not receive any information to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "the contrary by the end of this month.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "By this proposition I do not intend to force an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "issue but I would like to discuss a subject like this with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "scientific friends of mine, which I cannot do as long as I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "am bound by my promise to you.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "With very kind regards,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Yours Truly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
